          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Continuation of Useful Resources to States Act or COURTS Act</b></p> <p>This bill extends and otherwise revises funding for programs related to child welfare. Specifically, the bill</p> <ul> <li>extends funding through FY2022 for the Promoting Safe and Stable Families Program;</li> <li>extends funding through FY2022 for, and otherwise revises, the grant program for improving courts' handling of foster-care and adoption proceedings; and</li> <li>provides funding for the Temporary Assistance for Needy Families (TANF) Contingency Fund for FY2019 and decreases the amount&nbsp;of funding available to the fund for&nbsp;FY2018.</li></ul>]]></text>
